reviewText: Wonderful, Totally enjoyable, Clean Christian humor.
If you enjoy church humor you will enjoy this.  He made me laugh at myself and foster an attitude I needed.

We loved watching it and our friends also loved it.  Dennis is the best comedian I'
ve seen in years.  His comedy is true to life.  We especially like his spiritually endings.

A commedian that is funny without cussing!  Awesome!  I', a fan for life!  It  just shows that christian commedians can be just as funny as other commedians.  This is not my first time hearing Dennis Swanberg.  It won:t be my last.  Cheers to Amazon for selling it.

Included are:
Remote Control
Struck by "The Call"
The Zipper Revenge
Baptismal Drain
Sweetheart's Special
Easter Sunday Surprise
and more.
